pageContext.claim: “if Sleepy Joe Biden ever got in, China would own the United States. They'd own it. They'd own every one of these people. They'd own this building. They'd own the United States -- because Biden would give them everything for two reasons: Number one, he's not smart; and number two, he's weak. China would own our country.”
pageContext.analysis: This is over-the-top political rhetoric, aimed at suggesting Biden has business ties to China. (There is no evidence of that.) The United States would not be "owned" by China if Biden is elected.
